{"query": "At the counter or automated pay station, the customer can scan the on-display QR code to connect their profile.", "category": "checkout_support", "file_name": "payment_issues.txt"}
{"query": "The customer can use the TelMart application scanner or their phone camera to scan the QR code for TelMart Money service.", "category": "checkout_support", "file_name": "payment_issues.txt"}
